com.google.api.client.json.jackson

Class JacksonParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.client.json.JsonParser
      • com.google.api.client.json.jackson.JacksonParser

  • final class JacksonParser
extends JsonParser
    Low-level JSON serializer implementation based on Jackson.

    Implementation is not thread-safe.

    Author:
    Yaniv Inbar
